angular动画:
	AngularJS 使用动画需要引入 angular-animate.min.js 库。		
	var app = angular.module('myApp', ['ngAnimate']);
	
	ng-show
	ng-hide
	ng-class
	ng-view
	ng-include
	ng-repeat
	ng-if
	ng-switch
	
	ng-animate
	ng-hide-animate
	ng-hide-add (如果元素将被隐藏)
	ng-hide-remove (如果元素将显示)
	ng-hide-add-active (如果元素将隐藏)
	ng-hide-remove-active (如果元素将显示)